1 WHEREAS, the organization continues to advocate for national media
2 acknowledgment of coastal restoration efforts, infrastructure needs, and other issues that are
3 vital to the rebuilding of wetlands in Louisiana and along the Gulf Coast; and
4 WHEREAS, Women of the Storm is most deserving of the highest recognition for
5 its unrelenting pursuit of the restoration of the diverse communities along the Gulf Coast.
6 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
7 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend Women of the Storm on the occasion of its
8 twentieth anniversary and does hereby extend enduring appreciation for its members'
9 contributions to the communities along the Gulf Coast.
